Sorry for the delay.

@YaelDillies: the only new lemmas that use the existing definitions (`Finsupp.{tail/cons}`) are these two, which are about the relationship between `tail` and `update`. The rest are dependent on the new definitions (`Finsupp.{init/snoc/removeNth/insertNth}`).

Because of this, I'm not very sure if a dependent PR with two lemmas is of much use (though I'd be glad to do it if it helps).
